[[File:Germi Station.jpg|thumb|Weather Station at [[Germi]], Ardabil]]
==History== Serious efforts have been made to establish a [[meteorological station]] in the city of [[Germi]] since 2000 and in the spring of 2001, succeeded. The State Meteorological Organization has sent experts to locate and purchase place of Meteorological Station in the city of Germi. After going through the legal process, the construction of the station began and it began experimentation in February 2003. <ref name="irimo"/> <ref name="irimo"/> <ref name="weather.com">{{cite web|url=https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/Germi+Iran+IRXX0336:1:IR|title=Germi, Iran 10 Day Weather|website=weather.com|accessdate=2017-11-08}}</ref>
The [[Synoptic scale meteorology|Synoptic]] [[Meteorological]] Station of [[Germi]] city, on May 20, 2004, with the presence of local authorities officially opened and joined the network of weather stations of the country.<ref name="hakimpedia">{{cite web|url=http://hakimpedia.ir/wiki/|website=hakimpedia.ir|title=hakimpedia.ir/wiki/|accessdate=2017-11-08}}</ref>
==Station type== Germi Weather Station is a 12-hour synoptic station with an international code or ID 40714. <ref name="irimo"/>
==Activities== The activities of the synoptic meteorological station of Germi city include measurements of dry and wet temperatures, maximum and minimum air temperature, wind speed, wind speed and wind direction, amount of cloudy sky, evaporation rate, depth of depth of soil, minimum surface area, sunshine time (sun radiation), And measure the amount of rainfall (different forms of atmospheric precipitation), calculate the dew point and air humidity, and prepare timely reports of the parameters and transmit it to the provincial capital as well as provide various agricultural bulletins and monthly and weekly statistics.<ref name="hakimpedia"/> <ref name="weather.com"/> <ref name="worldweatheronline"/> <ref name="weather-atlas.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.weather-atlas.com/en/iran/germi-weather-tomorrow|title=Germi-weather-tomorrow|website=weather-atlas|accessdate=2017-11-08}}</ref> <ref name="havairan.com">{{cite web|url=http://en.havairan.com/weather/Ardabil/Germ%C4%AB|title=Weather Forecast Germi|website=havairan.com|accessdate=2017-11-14}}</ref> <ref name="tsear.ch">{{cite web|url=http://tsear.ch/posts/Germimet/250|title=Germi weather|website=tsear.ch|accessdate=2017-11-10}}</ref> <ref name="yourweatherservice">{{cite web|url=https://www.yourweatherservice.com/weather-14-days/germi/iran/irzz0223|title=Weather Germi|website=yourweatherservice.com|accessdate=2017-11-16}}</ref> <ref name="climate-data">{{cite web|url=https://fa.climate-data.org/location/5623/|title=climate-data|website=tsear.ch|accessdate=2017-11-16}}</ref> <ref name="timeanddate.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/@133972|title=Local Time in Germī, Iran|website=timeanddate.com|accessdate=2017-11-16}}</ref>
